title: SwiftTEA: All Too Well (The Short Film)
description:
It's another exciting day to be a Swiftie! Taylor continues to surprise us with her work! She knows how pumped everyone is for All Too Well so she's going to share even more than we expected.. Blondie understood the assignment!
Plus a new day, a new theory and Jimmy Fallon joins in on the Easter egg fun.
What song are you most excited about on Red? What did we miss in this episode? What else would you like to hear from us? There are lots of ways to reach us!
